{
  "stem": "3012.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was 1475 Walton Avenue in The Bronx.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we found that some very good friends were living in Rego Park in Queens.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there happened to be a vacancy in the same building, so we moved there in '64.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we have lived there-- I lived there with Mother and Auntie 'til October of '75.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then I moved here, and they stayed behind there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mother and Auntie started working in a sweat shop.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then gradually they worked up their way to Bloomingdale's, and they were doing finishing work in the alteration department-- patterns and all that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mother is excellent-- Mother was always excellent at sewing, and my aunt also has been very handy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I started working-- somebody recommended me to work as a store bookkeeper for an export agent-- export-import firm.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I hated it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, after the opera.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I figured well, Olga, you are in America.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You have to start, and then you'll see what happens.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I stayed there until-- from '62 'til '66.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "By that time, I was familiarized with all the agents, the opera houses, the concert bureaus, and all that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I had an interview with an agent-- a placement agent-- and he said that I have two jobs for you.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "One is at the Metropolitan Opera at the financial or administrative department, but not artistic administration-- technical administration.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If you want to do it, I can't guarantee you-- and then she repeated-- I cannot guarantee you you would be able to get into artistic administration.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "However, if you start working at Columbia Artists, that will give you a new perspective.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You can build up your contacts.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And you'll get an American concert experience.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I chose Columbia.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
